## Idea

An [[(âˆž,1)-monad]] such that applying to its unit its unit yields an [[equivalence]]. Exhibiting a [[reflective sub-(âˆž,1)-category]].

The [[(âˆž,1)-category]] refinement of a _[[idempotent monad]]_.

